a single thread of yarn, who embarks on a seemingly larger than
life journey through the breath-taking environments of
Northern Scandinavia

through different physics-based puzzles in this unique puzzle
platformer. Swing over a tree gap or hitch a ride on a flying
kite, no feat is too big. Along the way, witness Yarny unlock
